-- Shares in Italy's Monte Paschi extend loss, hit new all-time low
-- 
-- Thu Oct 16, 2014 07:39AM EDT
-- None



MILAN, Oct 16 (Reuters) - Shares in Italy's third biggest lender, Banca Monte dei Paschi di Siena <BMPS.MI> fell more than 12 percent on Thursday afternoon, extending losses suffered earlier this week.

